Portugal May Add Tax on Electricity Consumption, Diario Reports

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-10-13T06:52:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/portugal-may-add-tax-on-electricity-consumption-diario-reports.html
The Portuguese government may
introduce a new tax on electricity consumption, Diario Economico
reported, without saying how it obtained the information.  For a family with an annual consumption of about 5
megawatt-hours, the cost of the tax may be about 12 or 13 euros
a year, the Portuguese newspaper said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
